answers.question: Tell me about yourself. What interests you about this role?
answers.answer_text: Hello, my name is Vishwas Kumar Keshri and I am currently pursuing BTEC from the NSH University. I have keen interest in artificial intelligence and machine learning. I have also secured courses from Korsera which was affiliated by IBM in machine learning algorithms and Python. I have also made many projects like stock price prediction, driver draws in as a detection which are based on deep learning and machine learning where I have learned many usage of model evaluation, hyper parameter tuning and how the neural network works. So that's about me.
